	      &lt;/div&gt;
	      - P.E.T. Change-log: Stay up-to-date with the changes to P.E.T. by reading the official developer change-logs!&lt;/div&gt;
	      &lt;/div&gt;
	      - Phasmophobia Change-log: Stay up-to-date with the changes to Phasmophobia by reading the official developer change-logs!&lt;/div&gt;
	      &lt;/div&gt;
	      App Settings:&lt;/div&gt;
	      Ability to disable Mobile Data usage for the Message Center.&lt;/div&gt;
